 $30)<x id=\\\"gid_4\\\"/>Bedouin camp visit<x id=\\\"gid_5\\\"/>Traditional Bedouin bread baking demonstration<x id=\\\"gid_6\\\"/>Soft drink during sunset and dinner<x id=\\\"gid_7\\\"/>Seasonal fruits (2 different kinds)<x id=\\\"gid_8\\\"/>30-minute quad bike ride (if option selected)<x id=\\\"gid_9\\\"/>Experienced desert guide<x id=\\\"gid_10\\\"/>FTS Organic oils - 100% pure (Optional add-on - $10)<x id=\\\"gid_11\\\"/>Traditional BBQ dinner with 5 hot dishes\",\"translated_content\":\"萨赫尔哈什或马卡迪湾酒店接送服务<x id=\\\"gid_0\\\"/>萨赫尔哈什沙漠骆驼骑行<x id=\\\"gid_1\\\"/>FTS围巾（可选附加项目 - 10美元）<x id=\\\"gid_2\\\"/>观星体验，配备高倍望远镜及星空导览<x id=\\\"gid_3\\\"/>每人共享摄影师服务（可选附加项目 - 30美元）<x id=\\\"gid_4\\\"/>贝都因营地参观<x id=\\\"gid_5\\\"/>传统贝都因面包烘焙演示<x id=\\\"gid_6\\\"/>日落时分及晚餐时的软饮<x id=\\\"gid_7\\\"/>时令水果（2种）<x id=\\\"gid_8\\\"/>30分钟四轮摩托车骑行（如选择该选项）<x id=\\\"gid_9\\\"/>经验丰富的沙漠向导<x id=\\\"gid_10\\\"/>FTS有机油 - 100%纯天然（可选附加项目 - 10美元）<x id=\\\"gid_11\\\"/>传统烧烤晚餐，含5道热菜\",\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_3_0_0__12\",\"context\":\"\",\"word_count\":74,\"unclear\":false,\"kind\":\"seg\",\"extras\":{\"type\":\"custom_field\",\"unit\":\"\",\"group\":\"Custom Fields\",\"xpath\":\"text()[13]\",\"page_id\":96141087,\"group_id\":\"Custom_Fields-0\",\"html_tags\":[],\"main_html_tag\":null,\"wpml_suggested_tm\":true},\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:04.000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:04.000Z\",\"minimized_artifacts\":{\"gid_0\":[{\"name\":\"ctype\",\"value\":\"x-html-wpml_linebreak\"},{\"name\":\"id\",\"value\":\"gid_0\"}],\"gid_1\":[{\"name\":\"ctype\",\"value\":\"x-html-wpml_linebreak\"},{\"name\":\"id\",\"value\":\"gid_1\"}],\"gid_2\":[{\"name\":\"ctype\",\"value\":\"x-html-wpml_linebreak\"},{\"name\":\"id\",\"value\":\"gid_2\"}],\"gid_3\":[{\"name\":\"ctype\",\"value\":\"x-html-wpml_linebreak\"},{\"name\":\"id\",\"value\":\"gid_3\"}],\"gid_4\":[{\"name\":\"ctype\",\"value\":\"x-html-wpml_linebreak\"},{\"name\":\"id\",\"value\":\"gid_4\"}],\"gid_5\":[{\"name\":\"ctype\",\"value\":\"x-html-wpml_l