 as the sun begins its descent.\",\"translated_content\":\"Arrive at the edge of the golden dunes and wrap yourself in a traditional Egyptian scarf for style and sun protection. Mount your gentle camel for a serene ride through the silent, rolling sands, feeling the timeless rhythm of desert travel as the sun begins its descent.\",\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_46_0_0\",\"context\":\"\",\"word_count\":21,\"unclear\":false,\"kind\":\"seg\",\"extras\":{\"type\":\"custom_field\",\"unit\":\"\",\"group\":\"Custom Fields\",\"xpath\":\"text()[1]\",\"page_id\":96141087,\"group_id\":\"Custom_Fields-0\",\"html_tags\":[],\"auto_joined\":true,\"main_html_tag\":null},\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:07.000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:04.000Z\",\"minimized_artifacts\":null,\"missing_markers\":[],\"credits_count\":21,\"can_join_to\":null,\"joined_group\":{\"id\":564284117,\"parent_mrk_id\":7981804533,\"wpml_trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit__0__1\",\"minimized_artifacts\":{},\"word_count\":47,\"children\":[{\"id\":7981804533,\"signature\":\"ca10154575da2218f112833843cfe08f\",\"word_count\":21,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_46_0_0\",\"target_content\":\"Arrive at the edge of the golden dunes and wrap yourself in a traditional Egyptian scarf for style and sun protection.\",\"original_content\":\"Arrive at the edge of the golden dunes and wrap yourself in a traditional Egyptian scarf for style and sun protection.\"},{\"id\":7981804534,\"signature\":\"9b8eeeada788e81ddb611d4c63cb4de2\",\"word_count\":26,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_46_0_1\",\"target_content\":\"Mount your gentle camel for a serene ride through the silent, rolling sands, feeling the timeless rhythm of desert travel as the sun begins its descent.\",\"original_content\":\"Mount your gentle camel for a serene ride through the silent, rolling sands, feeling the timeless rhythm of desert travel as the sun begins its descent.\"}],\"is_autojoined\":true}},{\"id\":7981804535,\"status\":0,\"original_content\":\"Disembark at a prime vantage point to witness one of Egypt's most breathtaking desert sunsets. Your guide will help you capture the perfect shot as the sky ignites in brilliant shades of orange and purple, painting the endless dunes in a golden hour glow. Sip a refreshing soft drink as you take in the panoramic view.\",\"translated_content\":\"Disembark at a prime vantage point to witness one of Egypt's most breathtaking desert sunsets. Your guide will help you capture the perfect shot as the sky ignites in brilliant shades of orange and purple, painting the endless dunes in a golden hour glow. Sip a refreshing soft drink as you take in the panoramic view.\",\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_47_0_0\",\"context\":\"\",\"word_count\":15,\"unclear\":false,\"kind\":\"seg\",\"extras\":{\"type\":\"custom_field\",\"unit\":\"\",\"group\":\"Custom Fields\",\"xpath\":\"text()[1]\",\"page_id\":96141087,\"group_id\":\"Custom_Fields-0\",\"html_tags\":[],\"auto_joined\":true,\"main_html_tag\":null},\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:07.000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:04.000Z\",\"minimized_artifacts\":null,\"missing_markers\":[],\"credits_count\":15,\"can_join_to\":null,\"joined_group\":{\"id\":564284119,\"parent_mrk_id\":7981804535,\"wpml_trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit__0__2\",\"minimized_artifacts\":{},\"word_count\":56,\"children\":[{\"id\":7981804535,\"signature\":\"4797932e148b175ef94a71aa4ea02136\",\"word_count\":15,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_47_0_0\",\"target_content\":\"Disembark at a prime vantage point to witness one of Egypt's most breathtaking desert sunsets.\",\"original_content\":\"Disembark at a prime vantage point to witness one of Egypt's most breathtaking desert sunsets.\"},{\"id\":7981804536,\"signature\":\"68c2e896c4ea7e16767ddfd0f67eb5e0\",\"word_count\":29,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_47_0_1\",\"target_content\":\"Your guide will help you capture the perfect shot as the sky ignites in brilliant shades of orange and purple, painting the endless dunes in a golden hour glow.\",\"original_content\":\"Your guide will help you capture the perfect shot as the sky ignites in brilliant shades of orange and purple, painting the endless dunes in a golden hour glow.\"},{\"id\":7981804537,\"signature\":\"c3553576c0acd3a9b70378802479652d\",\"word_count\":12,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_47_0_2\",\"target_content\":\"Sip a refreshing soft drink as you take in the panoramic view.\",\"original_content\":\"Sip a refreshing soft drink as you take in the panoramic view.\"}],\"is_autojoined\":true}},{\"id\":7981804538,\"status\":0,\"original_content\":\"Travel deeper into the desert to arrive at a welcoming Bedouin-style camp, illuminated by flickering lanterns and candles. Feel the authentic desert atmosphere envelop you as you're greeted with traditional hospitality. Listen to captivating stories of desert life and Bedouin traditions from your experienced guide around the warm campfire.\",\"translated_content\":\"Travel deeper into the desert to arrive at a welcoming Bedouin-style camp, illuminated by flickering lanterns and candles. Feel the authentic desert atmosphere envelop you as you're greeted with traditional hospitality. Listen to captivating stories of desert life and Bedouin traditions from your experienced guide around the warm campfire.\",\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_48_0_0\",\"context\":\"\",\"word_count\":19,\"unclear\":false,\"kind\":\"seg\",\"extras\":{\"type\":\"custom_field\",\"unit\":\"\",\"group\":\"Custom Fields\",\"xpath\":\"text()[1]\",\"page_id\":96141087,\"group_id\":\"Custom_Fields-0\",\"html_tags\":[],\"auto_joined\":true,\"main_html_tag\":null},\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:07.000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:04.000Z\",\"minimized_artifacts\":null,\"missing_markers\":[],\"credits_count\":19,\"can_join_to\":null,\"joined_group\":{\"id\":564284121,\"parent_mrk_id\":7981804538,\"wpml_trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit__0__2\",\"minimized_artifacts\":{},\"word_count\":50,\"children\":[{\"id\":7981804538,\"signature\":\"0ef85fa3ac614d6cdf9e64e15b1e291c\",\"word_count\":19,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_48_0_0\",\"target_content\":\"Travel deeper into the desert to arrive at a welcoming Bedouin-style camp, illuminated by flickering lanterns and candles.\",\"original_content\":\"Travel deeper into the desert to arrive at a welcoming Bedouin-style camp, illuminated by flickering lanterns and candles.\"},{\"id\":7981804539,\"signature\":\"82cba626c2d8d38f031012ab4017552f\",\"word_count\":13,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_48_0_1\",\"target_content\":\"Feel the authentic desert atmosphere envelop you as you're greeted with traditional hospitality.\",\"original_content\":\"Feel the authentic desert atmosphere envelop you as you're greeted with traditional hospitality.\"},{\"id\":7981804540,\"signature\":\"ab21137d29bc7bb346bc8133edb3d25b\",\"word_count\":18,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_48_0_2\",\"target_content\":\"Listen to captivating stories of desert life and Bedouin traditions from your experienced guide around the warm campfire.\",\"original_content\":\"Listen to captivating stories of desert life and Bedouin traditions from your experienced guide around the warm campfire.\"}],\"is_autojoined\":true}},{\"id\":7981804541,\"status\":0,\"original_content\":\"Roll up your sleeves and learn the ancient art of Bedouin bread baking over hot coals. Feel the warmth of the fire as you shape the dough, connecting with a culinary tradition passed down through generations. Watch traditional Bedouin performers bring the culture to life through captivating dance and music around the campfire.\",\"translated_content\":\"Roll up your sleeves and learn the ancient art of Bedouin bread baking over hot coals. Feel the warmth of the fire as you shape the dough, connecting with a culinary tradition passed down through generations. Watch traditional Bedouin performers bring the culture to life through captivating dance and music around the campfire.\",\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_49_0_0\",\"context\":\"\",\"word_count\":16,\"unclear\":false,\"kind\":\"seg\",\"extras\":{\"type\":\"custom_field\",\"unit\":\"\",\"group\":\"Custom Fields\",\"xpath\":\"text()[1]\",\"page_id\":96141087,\"group_id\":\"Custom_Fields-0\",\"html_tags\":[],\"auto_joined\":true,\"main_html_tag\":null},\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:07.000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:04.000Z\",\"minimized_artifacts\":null,\"missing_markers\":[],\"credits_count\":16,\"can_join_to\":null,\"joined_group\":{\"id\":564284122,\"parent_mrk_id\":7981804541,\"wpml_trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit__0__2\",\"minimized_artifacts\":{},\"word_count\":53,\"children\":[{\"id\":7981804541,\"signature\":\"a95fdd37793c7c98d894fcc8fd7d33fd\",\"word_count\":16,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_49_0_0\",\"target_content\":\"Roll up your sleeves and learn the ancient art of Bedouin bread baking over hot coals.\",\"original_content\":\"Roll up your sleeves and learn the ancient art of Bedouin bread baking over hot coals.\"},{\"id\":7981804542,\"signature\":\"76ec27ead4d4c00525b2ca678c8ab3fb\",\"word_count\":20,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_49_0_1\",\"target_content\":\"Feel the warmth of the fire as you shape the dough, connecting with a culinary tradition passed down through generations.\",\"original_content\":\"Feel the warmth of the fire as you shape the dough, connecting with a culinary tradition passed down through generations.\"},{\"id\":7981804543,\"signature\":\"8a79f1fa83f3a5c5cf32a3138b4a8209\",\"word_count\":17,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_49_0_2\",\"target_content\":\"Watch traditional Bedouin performers bring the culture to life through captivating dance and music around the campfire.\",\"original_content\":\"Watch traditional Bedouin performers bring the culture to life through captivating dance and music around the campfire.\"}],\"is_autojoined\":true}},{\"id\":7981804544,\"status\":0,\"original_content\":\"Savor a feast of five hot traditional dishes alongside seasonal fruits, enjoying authentic flavors in the open desert air. Your freshly baked bread is the perfect accompaniment. This traditional BBQ dinner under the stars, with the campfire crackling nearby, is a true highlight of Egypt desert tours.\",\"translated_content\":\"Savor a feast of five hot traditional dishes alongside seasonal fruits, enjoying authentic flavors in the open desert air. Your freshly baked bread is the perfect accompaniment. This traditional BBQ dinner under the stars, with the campfire crackling nearby, is a true highlight of Egypt desert tours.\",\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_50_0_0\",\"context\":\"\",\"word_count\":19,\"unclear\":false,\"kind\":\"seg\",\"extras\":{\"type\":\"custom_field\",\"unit\":\"\",\"group\":\"Custom Fields\",\"xpath\":\"text()[1]\",\"page_id\":96141087,\"group_id\":\"Custom_Fields-0\",\"html_tags\":[],\"auto_joined\":true,\"main_html_tag\":null},\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:07.000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:04.000Z\",\"minimized_artifacts\":null,\"missing_markers\":[],\"credits_count\":19,\"can_join_to\":null,\"joined_group\":{\"id\":564284123,\"parent_mrk_id\":7981804544,\"wpml_trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit__0__2\",\"minimized_artifacts\":{},\"word_count\":47,\"children\":[{\"id\":7981804544,\"signature\":\"79c1f0ec6be6d6cf9b63ab265eeef41d\",\"word_count\":19,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_50_0_0\",\"target_content\":\"Savor a feast of five hot traditional dishes alongside seasonal fruits, enjoying authentic flavors in the open desert air.\",\"original_content\":\"Savor a feast of five hot traditional dishes alongside seasonal fruits, enjoying authentic flavors in the open desert air.\"},{\"id\":7981804545,\"signature\":\"70940478cb871832d97fd4675d4aa190\",\"word_count\":8,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_50_0_1\",\"target_content\":\"Your freshly baked bread is the perfect accompaniment.\",\"original_content\":\"Your freshly baked bread is the perfect accompaniment.\"},{\"id\":7981804546,\"signature\":\"230d99b990386be8772723cf381f52c6\",\"word_count\":20,\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_50_0_2\",\"target_content\":\"This traditional BBQ dinner under the stars, with the campfire crackling nearby, is a true highlight of Egypt desert tours.\",\"original_content\":\"This traditional BBQ dinner under the stars, with the campfire crackling nearby, is a true highlight of Egypt desert tours.\"}],\"is_autojoined\":true}},{\"id\":7981804547,\"status\":0,\"original_content\":\"As the sky darkens into a velvet canvas, embark on a guided celestial tour. Peer through high-powered telescopes to explore distant galaxies, star clusters, and planets invisible to the naked eye. Expert guides will point out constellations and share the astronomy woven into Bedouin navigation and folklore, making this a premier desert stargazing experience.\",\"translated_content\":\"As the sky darkens into a velvet canvas, embark on a guided celestial tour. Peer through high-powered telescopes to explore distant galaxies, star clusters, and planets invisible to the naked eye. Expert guides will point out constellations and share the astronomy woven into Bedouin navigation and folklore, making this a premier desert stargazing experience.\",\"trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit_51_0_0\",\"context\":\"\",\"word_count\":14,\"unclear\":false,\"kind\":\"seg\",\"extras\":{\"type\":\"custom_field\",\"unit\":\"\",\"group\":\"Custom Fields\",\"xpath\":\"text()[1]\",\"page_id\":96141087,\"group_id\":\"Custom_Fields-0\",\"html_tags\":[],\"auto_joined\":true,\"main_html_tag\":null},\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:07.000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-18T23:31:04.000Z\",\"minimized_artifacts\":null,\"missing_markers\":[],\"credits_count\":14,\"can_join_to\":null,\"joined_group\":{\"id\":564284124,\"parent_mrk_id\":7981804547,\"wpml_trans_unit_id\":\"wpml_trans_unit__0__2\",\"minimized_artifacts\":{},\"word_count\":55,\"children\":[{\